Package io.codeleaf.config.spec

Provides the classes to load a specification.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Specification
    This represents a specification.
    SpecificationProvider
    This class is used to obtain specifications.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Specification.Setting
    Represents a setting within a specification.
    SpecificationProvider.Singleton
    Holder for a singleton, to obtain the singleton, use SpecificationProvider.get()
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidSettingException
    Thrown when a specification has a specific invalid setting.
    InvalidSpecificationException
    Thrown when the specification contains invalid settings.
    SettingNotFoundException
    Thrown when a specification does not contain the a specific setting.
    SpecificationFormatException
    Thrown if a specification is in an invalid format, and thus settings can't be read.
    SpecificationNotFoundException
    Thrown when the specification was not found.

Package io.codeleaf.config.spec Description

Provides the classes to load a specification.
